records.name: Villa Park Sun Island Resort - Complimentary One Way Domestic Transportation For Stays Of 7 Nights And More 01 April To 30 September 2025

descriptions.direction: Located in Nalaguraidhoo, Villa Park Sun Island Resort - Complimentary One Way Domestic Transportation for stays of 7 nights and more 01 April to 30 September 2025 is on a private beach. While the natural beauty of Ari Atoll and Dhigurah Beach can be enjoyed by anyone, those looking for an activity can check out Himendhoo Thila. Vakarufalhi Island Beach and Maafushivaru Island Beach are two other places to visit that come recommended. Windsurfing offers a great chance to get out on the surrounding water, or you can seek out an adventure with hiking/biking trails nearby.
descriptions.general: This little slice of paradise, Sun Island Resort & Spa, is a jewel among the Maldives hotels, offering invigorating activities and tranquillity. The Maldivian resort will captivate the heart with extraordinary experiences and unforgettable memories. All transfers to and from the hotel are arranged by the hotel team, please contact them directly upon receiving the hotel confirmation. Guests can cruise along the stunning sapphire lagoons by jet-ski, canoe, or catamaran, or explore the spectacular local scenery and unique culture with excursions to neighboring islands. Complimentary room upgrade offer: Book 31.05.25 a Deluxe Beach Villa and get a complimentary room upgrade to Sunset Deluxe Beach Villa or book Lagoon Beach Villa and get a complimentary stay at Lagoon Beach Pool Villa. Offer valid for stays between 23.05.25 and 30.09.25.
